					<description><![CDATA[<p>Strategic gamers will enjoy calling upon heroes of varying abilities to protect their stronghold from waves of enemies. In this exciting game, you can randomly call multiple heroes with powerful defenses that can be upgraded to form your unique strategy. CONNECT WITH CUTE AND...</p>
